oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Eight Big Shows
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Buddy Lee Attractions, Inc.; Grand Ole Opry (Radio program); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising 8 big country - western and Grand Ole Opry shows available through Buddy Lee Attractions, Inc.: The Jean Shepard Show, The Homesteaders and Marti Brown, The Lester Flatt Show, The Jimmy Martin Show, The Wilma Burgess Show with Ernie Ashworth and Bobby Harden, The Audrey Williams Show, Ben Smathers and Stoney Mountain Cloggers, and The Sheb Wooley - Ben Colder Show. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
